message.text:
Few Slots Left!

Don’t miss out on 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”. With the event on September 24, 2025, fast approaching. 

Join us at the 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦 for a day of inspiration, innovation, and networking in the hospitality and tourism industry.

𝐒𝐞𝐜𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐬𝐩𝐨𝐭 now and connect with industry leaders before the opportunity passes!

👉 Register today!
https://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=3F6kgO7V4EaddTfEe-m3zM3QzDs0peRLmijvCfcM1HlUNjRVQk9STTdVUU1LWTNWMUJQMlZWOEhVRS4u

Let’s shape the future together!

message.text:
Few Slots Left!

Don’t miss out on 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”. With the event on September 24, 2025, fast approaching. 

Join us at the 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦 for a day of inspiration, innovation, and networking in the hospitality and tourism industry.

𝐒𝐞𝐜𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐬𝐩𝐨𝐭 now and connect with industry leaders before the opportunity passes!

👉 Register today!
https://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=3F6kgO7V4EaddTfEe-m3zM3QzDs0peRLmijvCfcM1HlUNjRVQk9STTdVUU1LWTNWMUJQMlZWOEhVRS4u

Let’s shape the future together! 

#LimitedSlots #StartUpServeSoar #KawingProduction

message.text:
Few Slots Left!

Don’t miss out on 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”. With the event on September 24, 2025, fast approaching. 

Join us at the 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦 for a day of inspiration, innovation, and networking in the hospitality and tourism industry.

𝐒𝐞𝐜𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐬𝐩𝐨𝐭 now and connect with industry leaders before the opportunity passes!

message.text:
Few Slots Left!

Don’t miss out on 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”. With the event on September 24, 2025, fast approaching. 

Join us at the 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦 for a day of inspiration, innovation, and networking in the hospitality and tourism industry.

𝐒𝐞𝐜𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐬𝐩𝐨𝐭 now and connect with industry leaders before the opportunity passes!

👉 Register today!
https://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=3F6kgO7V4EaddTfEe-m3zM3QzDs0peRLmijvCfcM1HlUNjRVQk9STTdVUU1LWTNWMUJQMlZWOEhVRS4u

Let’s shape the future together! 

#LimitedSlots #StartUpServeSoar #KawingProduction

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

#WorldTourismDay2025
#SustainableTourism 
#FEU
#FEU97th
#FEUITHM
#EventuraProduction

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

#WorldTourismDay2025
#SustainableTourism 
#FEU
#FEU97th
#FEUITHM
#EventuraProduction

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

#WorldTourismDay2025
#SustainableTourism 
#FEU
#FEU97th
#FEUITHM
#EventuraProduction
